  RFC8897 [label="RFC8897
Requirements for Resource Public Key
Infrastructure (RPKI) Relying Parties
2020", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC8897.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document provides a single reference point for requirements for Relying Party (RP) software for use in the Resource Public Key Infrastructure (RPKI).  It cites requirements that appear in several RPKI RFCs, making it easier for implementers to become aware of these requirements.  Over time, this RFC will be updated to reflect changes to the requirements and guidance specified in the RFCs discussed herein."];
